OL,3,CMayors across the north could team up
OL,4,Cto take over Northern trains
OL,6,FNorth East mayor Kim McGuinness has
OL,7,Fsaid she and other mayors across the
OL,8,FNorth of England could try to seize
OL,9,Fcontrol of struggling rail services
OL,10,Fthat have "failed" passengers.
OL,12,FShe said she will team up with her
OL,13,Fmayoral colleagues to explore the
OL,14,Fpossibility of taking over Northern
OL,15,FTrains, under new Government plans to
OL,16,Fgive local leaders more powers.
