OL,3,CMayors across the north could team up
OL,4,Cto take over Northern trains
OL,6,FThe English Devolution White Paper,
OL,7,Funveiled by Deputy Prime Minister
OL,8,FAngela Rayner in December, outlines
OL,9,Fhow regional mayors will have a "clear
OL,10,Fright" to request more control over
OL,11,Ftrains, stations, and infrastructure
OL,12,F"up to full devolution of defined
OL,13,Flocal services".
