OL,3,CMayors across the north could team up
OL,4,Cto take over Northern trains
OL,6,FMs McGuinness told the Local Democracy
OL,7,FReporting Service (LDRS) that she
OL,8,Fbelieves such a system could allow her
OL,9,Fand her counterparts around the North
OL,10,Fof England, including the likes of
OL,11,FGreater Manchester's Andy Burnham and
OL,12,FYork and North Yorkshire Mayor David
OL,13,FSkaith, to collectively take over the
OL,14,Fheavily-criticised Northern franchise.
