OL,3,CMayors across the north could team up
OL,4,Cto take over Northern trains
OL,6,FNorthern runs around 2,500 local and
OL,7,Fregional services every day to towns
OL,8,Fand cities across the North, including
OL,9,Fthe recently-opened Northumberland
OL,10,FLine between Newcastle and Ashington,
OL,11,Fand is owned by the Department for
OL,12,FTransport's Operator of Last Resort
OL,13,Fafter being nationalised in 2020.
OL,15,FIts services have been plagued by
OL,16,Fcancellations and Northern was issued
OL,17,Fwith a formal breach notice last
OL,18,Fsummer because of its "unacceptable"
OL,19,Fperformance levels.
