OL,3,CMayors across the north could team up
OL,4,Cto take over Northern trains
OL,6,FNorthern's problems have been blamed
OL,7,Fon factors including high levels of
OL,8,Fsickness and a backlog of training, as
OL,9,Fwell as a lack of train crew
OL,10,Favailability on Sundays as the day
OL,11,Ffalls outside of some staff's
OL,12,Fcontracted working week.
