OL,3,CMayors across the north could team up
OL,4,Cto take over Northern trains
OL,6,FAsked if she would want to see mayors
OL,7,Ftake control over Northern, Ms
OL,8,FMcGuinness told the LDRS: "Absolutely.
OL,9,FUnapologetically, we are dead
OL,10,Fambitious for this region and control
OL,11,Fover train stations is something I was
OL,12,Fopen about wanting to have in this
OL,13,Fregion. Similarly, we will absolutely
OL,14,Fbe looking at regional proposals for
OL,15,Fcontrol of local rail because too many
OL,16,Fpeople are failed by poor service
OL,17,Flevels.
