OL,3,CMayors across the north could team up
OL,4,Cto take over Northern trains
OL,6,F"I always say that transport is not
OL,7,Fjust about getting from A to B, it is
OL,8,Fabout the infrastructure of
OL,9,Fopportunity and that is true right
OL,10,Facross the network. So we will be
OL,11,Flooking at opportunities to do that."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Northern said: "We
OL,14,Fare committed to working with directly-
OL,15,Felected mayors across our network to
OL,16,Ffind the optimal solution for
OL,17,Fpassengers as part of an integrated
OL,18,Fnetwork."
